      <ulink url="https://hunspell.github.io/">Voikko</ulink>, og
      <ulink url="https://github.com/unittest-cpp/unittest-cpp/releases">
        unittest-cpp</ulink> (nødvendig for tester)
    </para>

    <para condition="html" role="usernotes">Brukernotater:
